    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior paint remains vibrant with a healthy shine, though you will find some typical minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches from regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. Buyers can expect a dependable driving experience from a car that has been cared for properly throughout its life.",
