    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Mechanically beyond reproach and visually indistinguishable from new, this specimen is suited for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
